{"tid":1614152,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"萬花筒寫輪眼天照/加具土命可行方法","createTime":"2019-10-02T17:02:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-02T17:12:53.000Z","uid":163154,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"5d954b1faa6a892d1fdf3a26e8c80036de1de6cb","tid":1614152,"uid":163154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T17:02:00.000Z","msg":"眾所週知萬花筒寫輪眼既天照火係世間不能熄滅既火種<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家有無諗過漫畫內可以配合埋加具土命去移動不能熄滅既火<br />\n<br />\n天照用法=先用寫輪眼（復仇之眼）瞄準目標，再用意念將個目標表面化上一層電油或更高燃燒物質，再慢慢用血輪眼擊中目標輕輕點火🔥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n加具土命用法=對已燃燒既物體 用血輪眼aim住塗上電油或易燃物料轉移火種🔥 爽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">P.S.此post純屬動漫及學術討論 大家現實千祈千祈唔好嘗試<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"3782d97a7763ef85d31d97ed21eeae5b989057af","tid":1614152,"uid":163154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T17:02:34.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2890f152ea5c10ed557a36eb49e33bc991decd24","tid":1614152,"uid":163154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T17:04:02.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e65abd0f9eb5a8ec8d942d1de5c8e09893722e9","tid":1614152,"uid":298385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T17:12:53.000Z","msg":"1999<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}